Typealiases

The following typealiases are available globally.

  • JSONOptionalArrayTransaction

    A concrete JSONOptionalTransaction type that accepts an optional JSON payload that—if present—is expected to yield an NSArray.

    Declaration

    Swift

    public typealias JSONOptionalArrayTransaction = JSONOptionalTransaction<NSArray>
  • JSONOptionalDictionaryTransaction

    A concrete JSONOptionalTransaction type that accepts an optional JSON payload that—if present—is expected to yield an NSDictionary.

    Declaration

    Swift

    public typealias JSONOptionalDictionaryTransaction = JSONOptionalTransaction<NSDictionary>
  • JSONDictionaryTransaction

    A concrete JSONTransaction type that attempts to generate an NSDictionary from JSON data returned by the wrapped transaction.

    Declaration

    Swift

    public typealias JSONDictionaryTransaction = JSONTransaction<NSDictionary>
  • JSONArrayTransaction

    A concrete JSONTransaction type that attempts to generate an NSArray from JSON data returned by the wrapped transaction.

    Declaration

    Swift

    public typealias JSONArrayTransaction = JSONTransaction<NSArray>
  • PlatformImageType

    Represents the image type appropriate for the runtime platform. On iOS and tvOS, PlatformImageType is UIImage; on Mac OS X, it is NSImage.

    Declaration

    Swift

    public typealias PlatformImageType = UIImage
